sequenceDiagram
  participant Editor as Editor_SUZ
  participant CMS as Bitrix_CMS
  participant Outbox as Outbox
  participant Ingest as Sufler_Ingest
  participant RAG as RAG_Index
  Editor->>CMS: Публикация или изменение
  CMS->>CMS: Маппинг status scope body
  CMS->>Outbox: Полный payload
  Outbox->>Ingest: POST webhook
  Ingest-->>Outbox: 202 accepted
  Ingest->>RAG: Индексация из payload
